{"tid":1927263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莊思敏視像婚禮　家中簽紙嫁台灣男友！！！","createTime":"2020-03-15T16:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T16:45:26.000Z","uid":209657,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce3157fc5a33201cb7c0e29b7ee0e963a6a4ac2","tid":1927263,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1584280924_vM-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1584280924_vM-1280w.jpg&h=b767570e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恭喜！恭喜！39歲的莊思敏今日與台灣珍珠奶茶店老闆楊秉逸註冊結婚。受到疫情影響，二人在家中舉行簽字儀式，而雙方家長亦都只透過視像越洋見證他們的婚禮。雖然婚禮一切從簡，但有份出席的香港親友仍感到非常開心。"},{"pid":"ada6b66a33cb317b34be5592b36d53a28c3b4d28","tid":1927263,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1584280952_OC-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1584280952_OC-1280w.png&h=fdae0142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">思明接得花球！！！</span>"},{"pid":"5d9777a7ef1c4b9ca13c308043839b5128f6205c","tid":1927263,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1584283128_mR-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1584283128_mR-1280w.png&h=535ad625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">思明接過花球後即向楊明撒嬌，楊明即搞笑說道︰「哎呀！係咪有魚絲係入面，咁準嘅！」二人即笑過不停</span>。思明坦言她是內定接花球的人，並謂已與楊明有共識，暫以事業為重，儲多點錢讓未來生活更穩定。"},{"pid":"53eaf8fd5c12d5b895774823c0730176838d868e","tid":1927263,"uid":235535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"咁醜 不了"},{"pid":"103deb3b8e7d56fa85f409e6df6cefe8d2fefeb1","tid":1927263,"uid":307619,"like"